The,Spirent,TestCenter,REST,API,can,be,used,by,web,applications,in,order,to,perform,system,tests,in,virtual,cloud,environments,Using,the,REST,API,developers,can,specific,a,sequence,of,steps,to,test,or,automate,tasks,and,execute,for,quick,monitoring,results,This,is,applicable,for,scenarios,where,developers,need,to,monitor,a,virtual,switch,or,router